{{template "layout" .}}

{{define "title"}}off route — {{$.Site.Brand.Brand}}{{end}}

{{define "content"}}
<header class="off-route-wrap">
  <section class="off-route-panel">
    <div class="off-route-copy">
      <p class="off-route-kicker"><span>OFF ROUTE</span><i></i> POSITION / UNKNOWN</p>
      <h1>这条路线<br><em>不在赛道上。</em></h1>
      <p>地址可能从未存在，也可能已经离开历史。残局还没结束，回到主路线继续推进。</p>
      <a class="lancer-primary off-route-action" href="/">回到主路线 <b>↗</b></a>
    </div>
    <div class="off-route-code" aria-hidden="true">
      <span>ROUTE ERROR</span>
      <strong>404</strong>
      <div><i></i><b>RECALCULATING</b><i></i></div>
      <small>{{.Path}}</small>
    </div>
  </section>
</header>
{{end}}